review_data.title: Nicht gefunden
review_data.content: Diese Restaurant gibt es nicht oder die Adresse ist falsch... An der angegebenen Adresse ist ein anderes Restaurant.

review_data.title: Good but overpriced
review_data.content: Overall the food and service was a good experience, but the dishes were definitely overpriced relative to the portion size. The use of salt was also a bit liberal. I recommend the hot and sour prawn starter and the Chicken chettinad in any case.
